// Copy this file to `Secrets.xcconfig` in the same directory and paste
// your Google AI Studio key as the value of `GEMINI_API_KEY`. The
// destination file (`Secrets.xcconfig`) is gitignored so the key never
// leaves your machine via git.
//
// Generate a key at https://aistudio.google.com/apikey. The key is
// embedded in the app binary at build time and reaches Gemini directly
// from the iOS app — see ios/CLAUDE.md "API keys and Secrets.xcconfig".

GEMINI_API_KEY =

// gnews.io key for the swipe-driven news reader. Free key at https://gnews.io.
// Embedded at build time and called directly from the app (the phone can't
// reach the local FastAPI backend). Same pattern as GEMINI_API_KEY above.

GNEWS_API_KEY =

// Shared pairing secret for local device-to-device keyword sync (Multipeer Connectivity).
// Any string shared by your own devices — the sync only connects to devices presenting the
// same secret, so the app won't pair with a stranger's device on a shared (e.g. workplace)
// network. Optional: a built-in default is used when blank. Set your own for a private group.

SYNC_SECRET =
